The ability to work in a dynamic, fast-paced, work environment 
Solid project management skills 
Experience in building strong teams 
Experience with SAP HANA (Native HANA), SAP ECC, SAP BW 
Solid experience with SQL 
Experience using several of the following: Agile; Data Warehousing; SAP/BW/Business Objects; SQL; Data Modeling; Data flow mapping; Source to target mapping; Requirements gathering and data analysis; Microsoft BI Suite; Tableau; Testing & data validation techniques 
 
Education : 
B.S. degree in Information Systems or Information Technology, Computer Science, related fields of study. 
 
